metadata.title: Impact on  Population Density on Growth Rate of Walleye Pollock in the Aleutian Basin. Bull. Sea Fish. Inst.  Gdynia 1991, No. 1-2:22-30.
metadata.description: The otolith presents changes in length, age and girth of Pollock during 6 years of explanation of Pollock stock in Donut Hole.  General note of Pollock increased continually between 1985 and 1990
metadata.notes:
Purpose: Collect the information on the current state of exploited stock of Pollock in international water of the Bering Sea.
